title: Olympus Heights (IDW)
description:
Young Oliver Dobbs works for the local museum in Olympus Heights, Indiana. His world is turned upside down when he discovers that his reclusive next-door neighbor is, in fact, much more than a cranky old man who patrols the streets at night. When their paths collide, Oliver is thrust headfirst into a world of gods, ancient curses, and monster-hunting.



Released on http://ComicPirates.info
